extends layout

block content
  h2 Verify Your Email

  p We sent a 6-digit code to your email. Enter it below.

  if resent
    p Code resent successfully.

  if error
    p= error

  form(action="/verify-email", method="POST")
    input(type="text", name="code", placeholder="Enter 6-digit code", maxlength="6", required)
    button(type="submit") Verify

  form(action="/resend-verification", method="POST")
    button(type="submit") Resend Code